                            Other Search Options

   Use our other interfaces to search for data sets or related information
     __________________________________________________________________

   bullet  Search for Data -
          Enhanced Free-text Search

          + Perform Boolean, fielded, geospatial or temporal searches.

   bullet  Search for Related Information -
          Free-Text Search for Related Information

          + Search for information about data centers, campaigns or
            projects, platforms (sources) or instruments (sensors).

   bullet  Java Matrix Search Interface
          Dynamically generated search parameters. Requires a Java enabled
          browser. The Java Matrix Search Interface will be available by
          December 2001.[Posted: Sept. 26, 2001]
